  - Code: `pdd/server/budget.py`
  - Exports: `BudgetState`, `PddCommand`, `CommandResult`,
    `BudgetExceededError`, `parse_pdd_command`, `apply_command`,
    `format_startup_comment`, `format_settings_comment`, `should_halt`.
